OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781701875
OL,3,CEight-year-old's drawing to be shown
OL,4,Cbefore all Toy Story 5 screenings
OL,6,FAn eight-year-old says he felt "so
OL,7,Fmany emotions all at once" after being
OL,8,Ftold his picture would be shown ahead
OL,9,Fof all Toy Story 5 screenings.
OL,11,FTommy, from Blackpool, beat more than
OL,12,F1,000 entries to the British Board of
OL,13,FFilm Classification's (BBFC)
OL,14,Fcompetition, which will see his
OL,15,Fillustration shown alongside the
OL,16,Fofficial age rating before each UK
OL,17,Fshowing of the film.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
