OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781701875
OL,3,CEight-year-old's drawing to be shown
OL,4,Cbefore all Toy Story 5 screenings
OL,6,FReacting to his win, Tommy said: "I
OL,7,Fwas really shocked to win. I felt
OL,8,Fhappy, excited, amazed, so many
OL,9,Femotions all at once! I didn't believe
OL,10,Fit at first."
OL,12,FUsing acrylic paint and a mixture of
OL,13,Fbrushes and sponges, Tommy created a
OL,14,Fcolourful design featuring Toy Story
OL,15,Fcharacter's feet alongside Lilypad - a
OL,16,Ftablet, who is a new character for the
OL,17,Ffifth instalment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781701875
OL,3,CEight-year-old's drawing to be shown
OL,4,Cbefore all Toy Story 5 screenings
OL,6,F"I just wanted to make something
OL,7,Fcolourful, plus feet are easier to
OL,8,Fdraw than faces! I can't wait for my
OL,9,Ffriends to see it in the cinema,"
OL,10,FTommy added.
OL,12,FAs part of his prize, Tommy also got
OL,13,Fto travel to London for the UK Toy
OL,14,FStory fan event, where he walked the
OL,15,Fred carpet and was congratulated by
OL,16,Fthe film's stars, including Tom Hanks,
OL,17,Fwho voices Woody, and Tim Allen, who
OL,18,Fplays Buzz Lightyear.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781701875
OL,3,CEight-year-old's drawing to be shown
OL,4,Cbefore all Toy Story 5 screenings
OL,6,FOn seeing Tommy's design, two-time
OL,7,FOscar nominee Joan Cusack - the voice
OL,8,Fof cowgirl Jessie - said: "Did you
OL,9,Fdraw that? That's amazing!" while
OL,10,FLilypad actor Greta Lee told Tommy to
OL,11,F'keep up' the good work.
OL,13,FDirector Andrew Stanton was
OL,14,Fparticularly impressed, telling Tommy:
OL,15,F"You really did your homework... we'll
OL,16,Fhave to hire you someday!"
OL,18,FHe was then invited to an exclusive
OL,19,Fpreview of the film to see his Black
OL,20,FCard and signature appear on screen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781701875
OL,3,CEight-year-old's drawing to be shown
OL,4,Cbefore all Toy Story 5 screenings
OL,6,FThe nationwide competition called on
OL,7,Fchildren aged 4 to 11 to design the
OL,8,Fofficial BBFC Black Card for the film,
OL,9,FThe judging panel selected 11
OL,10,Ffinalists from 1,048 entries, before
OL,11,Fselecting Tommy as the winner.
OL,13,FDisney and Pixar's Toy Story 5 will be
OL,14,Fout in cinemas from 19 June. The
OL,15,Flatest instalment sees Woody, Buzz
OL,16,FLightyear and Jessie face the shift
OL,17,Ffrom traditional toys to modern tech.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
